  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "HR and Accounts Officer (Work From Home)",
  "description": "<p><strong>HR cum Accounts Officer (Part-Time, Remote)</strong></p><p>We are looking for a proactive and organized HR cum Accounts Officer to support our growing team. This part-time remote role is ideal for someone with HR/recruitment experience and basic accounting knowledge.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Source, screen, and schedule candidates</p></li><li><p>Maintain recruitment and HR records</p></li><li><p>Assist with onboarding and HR documentation</p></li><li><p>Support basic accounting tasks (data entry, invoices, expense tracking)</p></li><li><p>Maintain accounting and administrative files</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Experience in HR, recruitment, accounts, or administration</p></li><li><p>Strong communication and organizational skills</p></li><li><p>Proficient in MS Office / Google Workspace</p></li><li><p>Able to work independently and commit to a stable weekly schedule</p></li></ul><p><strong>What We Offer:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Flexible hours</p></li><li><p>Remote work</p></li><li><p>Friendly and supportive team</p></li></ul>",
